{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982340/extras/01_emotionaljourney.gif?t=1698419995\" /><br>Experience the poetic tale of a wolf cub and a fawn in the spectacular world of Blanc. Lost in a sudden snowstorm, they will have to lean on each other in order to follow the footprints their families left behind in the snow.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982340/extras/02_breathtakinghandcrafted.gif?t=1698419995\" /><br>Immerse yourself in the stunningly beautiful black-and-white world of Blanc \u2013 completely hand-drawn on paper in 2D before coming to life in 3D. Blanc focuses on the journey and experience of the animals with text-free gameplay and storytelling, allowing players to dive completely into its wondrous world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982340/extras/03_familiestracks.gif?t=1698419995\" /><br>Each animal has their own unique strengths that complements the other, which you\u2019ll need to make use of to navigate through the snowy landscapes. Using only two buttons and movement, this simple gameplay allows for anyone to play and follow their journey home.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982340/extras/04_cooperationrequire.gif?t=1698419995\" /><br>Two players take control of either the wolf cub or the fawn. Guide them through the environment, unforgiving weather, and obstacles that you must face together. Build a relationship together locally on the same screen or from far away with online play.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Unexpected encounter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1982340/52654d0261a03e44df0658e9c6b141191e142b66.jpg"},{"name":"Starting as a duo","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommun